a-averaged precipitation, which is already$\backslash$nbiased by its spatial resolution. However, comparison$\backslash$nbetween precipitation at Bucharest station and at its$\backslash$nnearest grid point shows that the performance of the ANN is$\backslash$nslightly better at gridpoint scale.},
